<tr><td colspan=2><font face="verdana, arial, geneva, helvetica" size="2">NEW YORK -- Sakonnet Technology, an energy-trading software and services provider, announced it has appointed Ian Clarke as director of product strategy for the Americas. Mr. Clarke was previously managing director of WeatherMarkets.com, a provider of weather forecasts and information to the energy and agricultural industries. Prior to that, he was manager of global commodity market coverage at Bloomberg. Sakonnet is backed by individual investors. </font><BR>
<a href="http://www.sknt.com" target="_new"><font face='arial,helvetica' size='2'>http://www.sknt.com</font></a>
